FBIS3-23478 "jptot013__l94006" JPRS-TOT-94-013-L Document Type:JPRS Document Title:Terrorism FOUO 21 March 1994 AFRICA SOUTH AFRICA Two Bombs in Ventersdorp 21-22 March Explosion in Service Station MB2103210094 Johannesburg SAPA in English 2035 GMT 21 Mar 94 MB2103210094 Johannesburg SAPA Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Ventersdorp March 21 SAPA -- A service station in rightwing-controlled Ventersdorp in the Western Transvaal has been damaged in an explosion, SABC [South African Broadcasting Corporation] radio news reported on Monday. Police confirmed that an explosive device had been used.
